    "stakeholders.0.desc":  "Beyond profit, the private sector brings innovation, investment, technology, and execution capacity to the urban environment. By partnering with governments, citizens, and institutions, we accelerate solutions and scale meaningful impact.",
    "stakeholders.1.title": "Citizens",
    "stakeholders.1.desc":  "We are artists, creators, makers, dreamers and civic, social and environmental entrepreneurs. Through openness, collaboration, creativity, and collective intelligence, communities co-create solutions that respond to real needs.",
